review_blob: Excellant.  Great example of a stout and there is clear indications as to why it won Gold in the SIBA awards.

Great beer.  Has to be a favoutite (even though it is not my highest score... go figure?)
Could stay on this all night... but shouldnt.  At 4.9% dangerous strength with sessionable qualities.
Apart from the lack of hop aroma, that I sometimes look for in a beer nowadays, this beer was utterly brilliant.  Decent session with enough flavour to stay on it all night.
